{"id":1770,"date":"2024-12-17T14:41:13","date_gmt":"2024-12-17T22:41:13","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/prowler.com\/?page_id=1770"},"modified":"2025-04-24T19:31:18","modified_gmt":"2025-04-25T02:31:18","slug":"azure","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/prowler.com\/azure\/","title":{"rendered":"Azure"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"block--hero relative pt-32 2xl:pt-28 mx-break-out px-break-out grid grid-cols-1 bg-dark min-h-[600px] lg:min-h-hero xl:min-h-screen overflow-x-hidden place-content-center pb-8\">\n                <img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1728\" height=\"1131\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/hero-grid-large-center-trimmed.svg\" class=\" object-cover absolute inset-0 object-center h-full pointer-events-none w-full z-0 ar-landscape\" alt=\"hero grid large center trimmed\" \/>        <div class=\"relative z-10\">\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column flex flex-col justify-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Seamless<mark x-data=\"{ visible: false }\" x-intersect=\"visible = true\" class=\"c-highlight\" :class=\"{ 'is-visible': visible }\"><span>Microsoft Azure<\/span><\/mark> Security<\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p>Prowler and Azure combine forces to deliver unparalleled cloud security, providing you with the tools and insights you need to protect your infrastructure. Together, they help you stay ahead of threats, ensure compliance, and achieve peace of mind.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons mt-8.5 is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-outline is-style-outline--1\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/cloud.prowler.com\/sign-up\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Sign Up + Connect Azure<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/prowler-screenshot-user-detail.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-484\"\/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group e-lines-y e-break-out-to-lines\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns e-accent-divider py-32 e-reverse-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column flex flex-col justify-center items-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group md:max-w-sm 2xl:max-w-md\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Different Systems, One Platform. It\u2019s That Simple.<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Managing cloud security across multiple environments shouldn\u2019t feel like wrestling an octopus. Whether you&#8217;re running in AWS, Azure, or Google Cloud, Prowler makes it simple to keep your systems secure and compliant.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With built-in checks and customizable policies, Prowler gives you a clear view of your Azure security posture\u2014from misconfigured IAM roles to forgotten storage buckets\u2014without the headaches of jumping between tools.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column flex justify-center items-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full e-screenshot\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"3388\" height=\"1882\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/prowler5overview-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1701\" srcset=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/prowler5overview-2.png 3388w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/prowler5overview-2-600x333.png 600w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/prowler5overview-2-2048x1138.png 2048w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/prowler5overview-2-150x83.png 150w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/prowler5overview-2-768x427.png 768w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/prowler5overview-2-1536x853.png 1536w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/prowler5overview-2-346x192.png 346w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3388px) 100vw, 3388px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group e-lines-y e-break-out-to-lines\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns e-accent-divider py-32 is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-3 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column flex flex-col justify-center items-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group md:max-w-sm 2xl:max-w-md\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Seamless Integration<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Prowler integrates seamlessly with your Microsoft Azure accounts, making it easy to set up and manage. Our integration ensures that you get the most out of Azures native security features while enhancing them with Prowler\u2019s specialized checks and reporting.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column flex justify-center items-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full e-screenshot\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"3086\" height=\"1752\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Screenshot-2024-12-17-at-20.48.21.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1766\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Screenshot-2024-12-17-at-20.48.21.png 3086w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/w