-3 delay-500 pt-5 pb-10 px-6 flex flex-col transition ease-in duration-300 translate-y-5 opacity-0\"    :class=\"{ '!translate-y-0 !opacity-100': animate }\"\n>\n            <div class=\"self-end rounded-full bg-dark flex size-25 justify-center items-center mb-10\">\n            <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"59\" height=\"58\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/cog-icon.svg\" class=\" ar-square\" alt=\"cog icon\" \/>        <\/div>\n                <h4 class=\"text-white text-xl\">Customizable Policies<\/h4>\n                <p>Tailor security policies to fit your organization\u2019s specific requirements. Prowler allows you to customize checks and thresholds, ensuring your security measures align with your unique needs.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"block--simple-cta relative border-divider-dark border-y grid grid-cols-1 place-content-center min-h-screen lg:min-h-cta mx-break-out px-break-out\">\n            <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1728\" height=\"1131\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/cta-grid-left-focus.svg\" class=\" object-cover absolute inset-0 object-center size-full pointer-events-none z-0 ar-landscape\" alt=\"cta grid left focus\" \/>        <div class=\"relative z-10\">\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-6 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading h1\">Get <mark x-data=\"{ visible: false }\" x-intersect=\"visible = true\" class=\"c-highlight\" :class=\"{ 'is-visible': visible }\"><span>Started<\/span><\/mark><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready to enhance your AWS security with Prowler? Follow these simple steps to get started:<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"block--numbered-list\">\n    <ol class=\"space-y-10\">\n                 